<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #0056D6;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .content h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #0056D6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0056D6;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #0056D6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <strong>
                <%= storeName %>
            </strong>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Subscription Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>Hello <%= storeOwnerName %>,</p>
            <p>Weâ€™re excited to have you on board with <strong><%= storeName %></strong>.</p>
            <p>Here are the details of your subscription:</p>
            <ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
                <li><strong>Start Date:</strong> <%= subscriptionStartDate %></li>
                <li><strong>Free Trial End Date:</strong> <%= trialEndDate %></li>
                <li><strong>Next Billing Date:</strong> <%= nextBillingDate %></li>
                <li><strong>Monthly Fee:</strong> KES 300</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Payment can be made via the following channels:</p>
            <ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
                <li><strong>Mpesa Paybill:</strong> <%= mpesaPaybill %></li>
                <li><strong>Account Reference:</strong> <%= accountReference %></li>
            </ul>
            <p>For any inquiries or assistance, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing <strong><%= storeName %></strong>. We look forward to supporting your business growth!</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= dashboardLink %>" class="button">Access Your Dashboard</a>
            </p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The <%= storeName %> Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 <%= storeName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><a href="https://example.com/unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="https://example.com/support">Support</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
